For hardware-based implementations, the following components are required:

### Integrated Circuits (ICs):
- IC 40110 (7 pcs)
- IC 4060
- IC 4013
- IC LM358
- IC 7805 (With heatsink)

### Display & Indicators:
- 7-Segment Display (7 pcs)
- LED

### Transistors & MOSFETs:
- Transistor 2N2222 (2 pcs)
- MOSFET IRFZ44N

### Passive Components:
- Crystal 4 MHz

### Capacitors:
- 100nF (3 pcs)
- 100uF (2 pcs)
- 220pF (2 pcs)

### Resistors:
- 470 ohm (50 pcs)
- 6.8K
- 10K
- 20K
- 1K
- 2M
- 120K
- 5.6K
- 3.3K (2 pcs)
- 150 ohm
- 100K
- 82K
- 680K

### Other Components:
- Push Tactile Switch (6 pins)
- IC Socket 8 pins
- IC Socket 14 pins
- IC Socket 16 pins (8 pcs)
- ZIF Socket 14 pins
